  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'In an isolated forest cut off from the outside world, a sudden crisis
    has shattered the peace of the campsite.



    Zombies have taken over the forest
    area, and survivors are trapped in different tents and camps, waiting to be rescued.
    The player takes on the role of Ryan, a rescue agent who enters this dangerous
    forest to find the survivors and bring them safely back to the safe house.



    This
    is not a mission that can be completed through combat alone. Zombies wander throughout
    the forest and will chase the player once they are detected. The player must
    not only clear the threats, but also decide when to fight, when to move, and
    when to protect the survivors.



    Your mission is to:



    Explore the
    forest.

    Defeat the zombies.

    Rescue the survivors.

    Return to the
    safe house.

    Complete the evacuation mission.



    In this forest, the
    true goal is not only to eliminate the enemies, but also to make sure every survivor
    is rescued.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
