      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "[Easy Mode]\n\r\nUse the mouse to adjust your view, and use WASD to control
    your character\u2019s movement.\r\n\r\nClick the left mouse button to attack
    zombies. When you are near a survivor tent, press F to rescue the survivor.\r\n\r\nAfter
    rescuing all survivors and defeating all zombies, return to the safe house to
    win the game.\r\n\r\nIf your character\u2019s health reaches zero, the game is
    over.\r\n\r\n\r\n[Hard Mode]\n\r\nIn Hard Mode, zombies will counterattack after
    being hit.\r\n\r\nYou can use the mouse wheel to switch weapons. When using a
    ranged weapon, zombies cannot attack you if you keep enough distance from them.\r\n\r\nPlease
    note: the ranged weapon, the crossbow, only has 5 arrows, so use them wisely.\r\n\r\nEnergy
    potions are hidden in certain areas of the map. Touch them to restore health.\r\n\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
